  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Fruit Tree 101&quot; is a program that creates thriving fruit tree orchards in schoolyards around the world so students have a source of improved nutrition and environmental education. The outdoor edible classrooms not only help clean and beautify campuses while providing a source of fresh, sustainable, healthy nutrition, but they also give teachers an excuse to hold class outside! Each donation is a vote for the importance of environmental education, access to fresh fruit, and time spent outdoors.</narrative>
  </description>
